12a758d80dca77c52d5a17c9c2b286bdc537dee5.query:
SELECT
            event_log.created_at
        FROM
            event_log
        JOIN
            closed_cfds on closed_cfds.id = event_log.cfd_id
        WHERE
            closed_cfds.uuid = $1
        ORDER BY event_log.created_at ASC
        LIMIT 1

                uuid as "uuid: model::OrderId"

b48bdec5e2f996ff75fc8e04e6759b45e0f41d10.query:
update EVENTS
                set
                    data = (
                        select json_set(events.data, '$.dlc', null)
                        from events as inner_events
                        where inner_events.id = EVENTS.id 
                    )
                where name = $1
                  and json_extract(EVENTS.data, '$.dlc') is not null
                  and id not in (
                    select max(id) from EVENTS as inner_events
                    where inner_events.cfd_id = EVENTS.cfd_id
                      and inner_events.name = EVENTS.name
                );

            cets.payout as "payout: model::Payout",
            cets.price as "price: model::Price"

ea5ee54109864160866708b764282b9d8d20cbf5.query:
update EVENTS
                set
                    data = (
                        select json_set(events.data, '$.dlc', null)
                        from events as inner_events
                        where EVENTS.id = inner_events.id
                    )
                where name = $1
                  and json_extract(EVENTS.data, '$.dlc') is not null
                  and cfd_id in (
                    select distinct cfd_id from EVENTS as inner_events
                        where inner_events.cfd_id = EVENTS.cfd_id
                        and inner_events.name = $2
                    );
